{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0001", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "知识分类目录: Secondary Quality Control System", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "知识分类目录: Secondary Quality Control System", "text": "本目录存放二级品管制度相关文件。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0002", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "文件清单", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "文件清单", "text": "- 二級品管制度.pdf\n  - 文件名: `二級品管制度.pdf`\n  - 文件类型: PDF\n  - 文件编号: `PO-PACIQADT-001`\n  - 文件名称: 二級品管制度\n  - 版本: `1.2`\n  - 生效日期: `2025-08-04`"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0004", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "1. 文件背景与目的", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "1. 文件背景与目的", "text": "- 为使工厂生产的订单货品达到客人品质要求，减少投诉及退货，推动工厂建立二级品质管理制度。\n- 在成品入胶袋前设置一道 100% 品质查验工序，由二级品管员执行，并通过合格证编号追溯原因与责任。\n- 通过制度推行，强化工厂品质控制责任感并提升客户满意度。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0005", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "2. 责任分工", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "2. 责任分工", "text": "- 相关部门负责制度编订、检讨、推行与执行效果监控。\n- 工厂按要求执行二级品管制度。\n- 二级相关部门由工厂高层直接管理，质检相关部门负责考核，不受生产车间管辖。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0006", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "3. 人员资格要求", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "3. 人员资格要求", "text": "- 新入职或调职的二级品管员须先接受上岗培训。\n- 经考核合格后方可上岗。\n- 相关考核记录需保留备查。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0007", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "4. 工作要求", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "4. 工作要求", "text": "- 每位二级品管员应有固定查货编号，并登记姓名与编号，不可随意更改。\n- 查货过程中需按疵点分类记录问题。\n- 发现问题时须退回上道工序返工，直至重检合格。\n- 每个工作日下班前需向相关主管反馈较严重疵点，以便及时改善。\n- 每张单完成查货后，应汇总该单疵点并统计品质情况。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0008", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "5. 考核机制", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "5. 考核机制", "text": "- 工厂质检相关部门每月应对二级品管员进行岗位考核，并保留合格记录。\n- 相关部门在下厂执行半成品或成品查验时，应每季度抽查一次工厂二级品管员的品质记录与考核记录。\n- 相关部门应结合现场查货发现的品质情况，每季度统计分析一次工厂二级品管工作表现。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0009", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "6. 实施与检讨", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "6. 实施与检讨", "text": "- 制度经总经理批准后实施。\n- 至少每年检讨一次。\n- 如执行过程中或检讨时需修订，由相关部门修订并呈报批签。"}
{"chunk_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6:0010", "doc_id": "markdown-07b9bbd5ddb6", "source_path": "references/knowledge_base/Secondary Quality Control System/data_structure.md", "file_type": "markdown", "business_category": "secondary_quality_control_system", "heading": "备注", "location_label": "section", "location_value": "备注", "text": "- 本条目已依据 `二級品管制度.pdf` 全文提取整理。\n- 文中带 `*` 的章节为本次修订版本新增或修改内容。"}
